<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="U" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Unusual" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Unusual,</orth> not customary, uncommon: <cit><quote>at an u. hour,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 5.463" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 463</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>some comet or u. prodigy,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.98" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 98</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>these your u. weeds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 1</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>strange u. blood, when man's worst sin is, he does too much good,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 4.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 2, 38</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>in u. pleasure,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 2.1.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 1, 13</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>u. vigilance,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 2.3.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 3, 4</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>